---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="CV">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8 px-4">


    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-1">Skills</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-1">
        <li><span class="font-medium">DevOps:</span> Kubernetes (K3s), Linux (NixOS), Docker, GitOps (Flux), Nixpkgs Maintainer (torcs).</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Programming Languages:</span> Python, Java, Go, SQL, Haskell, Nix, HTML/CSS.</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Technologies:</span> Git, Django, Astro, Google Cloud Platform (GCP).</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-1">Awards and Achievements</h2>
      
      <article class="mb-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Hack South West Hackathon 2026 - 2nd place</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/apex-hinde/HSW-garbo" class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:underline">github.com/apex-hinde/HSW-garbo</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-1">
          <li>Engineered a business logic platform in Go, integrating custom AI agent skills with a SQLite data layer to automate payroll and employee management.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Hack South West CTF 2025 - 2nd place</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-1">
          <li>Solved challenges in Network Forensics (WireShark), Linux exploitation, and scripting (Python) in a high-pressure competitive environment.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-1">Projects</h2>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Home Server</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/pixel-87/nixos-config" class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:underline">github.com/pixel-87/nixos-config</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-1">
          <li>Built and maintain 2 node cluster with Linux (NixOS) and Kubernetes (K3s).</li>
          <li>Set up and maintain applications for media, ad-blocking, web hosting, game server for 5+ users, automations.</li>
          <li>Implemented a GitOps workflow using Flux for my personal website, automating deployment.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Streak Buttons</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/pixel-87/duo-streak-widget" class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:underline">github.com/pixel-87/duo-streak-widget</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-1">
          <li>designed a Go microservice to generate personal streak buttons/widgets e.g. Duolingo, Github.</li>
          <li>Entirely cloud native, using Terraform to manage serverless GCP Cloud Run.</li>
          <li>Utilising CI for code quality through testing and linting.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Personal Website</h3>
          <a href="https://ed-thomas.dev" class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:underline">ed-thomas.dev</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-1">
          <li>Developed a personal developer website using Astro, HTML, CSS, JS.</li>
          <li>Write blog posts on various tech, to document my learning and share my journey.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Custom Split Ergonomic Keyboard</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/pixel-87/cantor-pixel" class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:underline">github.com/pixel-87/cantor-pixel</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-1">
          <li>Adapted and assembled a split ergonomic keyboard: soldering switches and microcontrollers, and configuring firmware.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-1">Experience</h2>

      <article class="mb-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap mb-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Excode Workshop Leader</h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 whitespace-nowrap">Sept 2025 — Nov 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">
          Google Developer Student Club (GDSC) — <a href="https://excode.co.uk" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">excode.co.uk</a>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
          <li>Co-lead beginner-friendly Python workshops.</li>
          <li>Guide 20+ students through practical exercises in fundamental, core Python concepts, program design, and debugging strategies.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap mb-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Onboarding Assistant</h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 whitespace-nowrap">June 2024 — Sept 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">
          Pembrokeshire County Council · Pembrokeshire, Wales
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
          <li>Streamlined daily workflow by developing a Python script to automate data filtering, reducing manual processing time by 60% and eliminating human error.</li>
          <li>Enabled system access for new employees, processing sensitive data in compliance with GDPR.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-6">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap mb-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">Social Secretary</h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 whitespace-nowrap">Sept 2024 — June 2025</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">
          University of Exeter Climbing Club
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
          <li>Organised weekly socials for 100+ people, coordinating with venues to schedule events and manage logistics.</li>
          <li>Taught new members climbing fundamentals and safety.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-1">Education</h2>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap mb-1">
           <h3 class="font-semibold">University of Exeter</h3>
           <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Exeter, England</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap mb-1">
           <span class="italic">BSc (Hons) Computer Science</span>
           <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Sept 2023 — May 2026</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
          <li>Predicted high 2:1.</li>
          <li>Relevant Modules: Data Structures, Software Development, Discrete Maths, Database Theory and design, Enterprise Computing, High Performance Computing, Data Science at Scale.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start flex-wrap mb-1">
           <h3 class="font-semibold">St. Michael's School</h3>
           <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Llanelli, Wales</span>
        </div>
         <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap mb-1">
             <span class="italic">A-Levels</span>
             <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Sept 2016 — June 2023</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
          <li>A-Levels: A*A*A (Maths, Physics, CS); AS-Level: A (Chemistry)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 pb-1">Certificates</h2>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
          <li>Github Foundations, Github</li>
        </ul>
        <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Oct 2025</span>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
